Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:26.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(438,550)}{\fs52}{\fad(0,540)}#20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:26.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1100,550)}{\fad(0,540)}口蜜腹剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论联络多少次都不接啊 巴纳比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还有关于晚餐秀事宜的面谈的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然让阿涅斯小姐为难..真是个可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由本人亲自去把他抓来 非让他跟你联络不可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托大家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人担心呢 漂亮脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那位巴纳比到底能不能成功办到呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐秀这种的演出..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..不 人家不是在担心那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作上那么严于律己的他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接电话什么的让人难以想象..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是陷入了什么麻烦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很常见的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候一定又会突然从哪冒出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮肤是偶像的命根子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像很欢乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么惩罚游戏呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 猛虎 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和巴纳比联络不上 你那边知道什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..诶诶？嗯喔..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩不会是又拌嘴了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？哪有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又干坏事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的“哪有啦”一点都不靠谱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猛虎先生的错对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事赶紧从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是马贝里克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难得呀 社长亲自打电话给我..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于巴纳比我有点事想单独和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉等下能麻烦你来一下我这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么兔子他怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实昨天晚上从他那给我打了通奇怪的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说了一句“一切的一切都无法相信了”就挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就联络不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他到底出了什么事 我认为你可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有想起什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实杀死兔子父母的并不是杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有不在场证明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们想重新整理一遍过去的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我把他给惹火了..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别像之前那样失去理智闯下大祸就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳比真幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个这么担心他的搭档在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有牛奶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又..有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..我突然觉得..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个东西..怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这玩意是我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里不知怎么给弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好险好险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重要的东西的说..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 诶？萨曼莎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 兔子的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白了 我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有熟人到了英雄事业部 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有张兔子的照片想给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 咖啡对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢您的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 萨曼莎小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚刚市内百货公司发生了恐怖爆炸事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上去救助那边的市民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和萨曼莎小姐的约..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她等一等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟她说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用超音速赶回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光天化日之下突然降临在顾客身上的惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的身影仍然无法确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！第一个到达现场的是正义的破坏王狂野猛虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来救你们 撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄来也 爷爷是狂野猛虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为救助行动要花上一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳您百忙之中..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会面已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样所有人都救出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦基！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦基！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！好像还有一位来不及逃出来的小朋友留在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个情况下已经..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的是也！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！那个是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦基..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后关头是这个男人 狂野猛虎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀~今天少有的帅气了一回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少有是什么意思啊少有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙真是没礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说就说“一如既往地帅气了一回”嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..危险危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我会处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是等不耐烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啥时候人不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我吓一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想着久违地一起吃顿晚餐结果你却突然昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也难怪 因为英雄是个累人的活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里算是我的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气 好好放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦 有买你的份啦 给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个..是兔子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？也就是说？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像把克莉姆所说的内容跟您说了之后..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天说了杰克杀害双亲的原因是偶然的入室杀人抢劫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一个成员的克莉姆死之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噬身之蛇这下算是被完全消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件就告一段落了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是罗伊兹 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂野猛虎说有紧急的事情要和社长说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要跟他讲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛虎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请接过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狂野猛虎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讲的事是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 关于今天拜访社长室的时候我捡到的别针
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个其实是兔子的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是两人买的是成对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我还错以为是自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长的房间里居然有兔子的别针
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成..兔子那家伙去了社长的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社长不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 说不定在那里卷入了什么麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么被弄乱之后的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯..没有那回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我现在去萨曼莎的家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没有见到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去确认一下照片的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会成为寻找兔子的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了点什么能马上联络我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那么打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个让人越发觉得愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划有变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了个有趣的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎彻先生遇到什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧 因为我们是搭档嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家紧急召集在一起不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于今后HeroTV的开展 我有重要的话跟你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 猛虎不是还没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那等大家都到齐了再..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟巴纳比我已经转达过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？巴纳比那小子已经找到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是身体不舒服卧床休息而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是猛虎先生的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么重要的话是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了让HeroTV继续兴隆下去的机密计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位先就此保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重要的事为什么让我们也出席？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得也应该告知一下和狂野猛虎朝夕相处的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是..什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个企划的主角是他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛虎他？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必说给我们听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么着急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在料理冷掉之前 我们先干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人大伤脑筋呢 往事被老调重谈..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴纳比终于开始能向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出这种事也只是让他白白受苦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候..真实还是被掩盖在黑暗之下为好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来再次给你植入设定好的记忆..让你继续过原来的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——这是原本的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是情况有点变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你担任新剧本中一个很重要的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对不起 萨曼莎小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就犯了困..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 罗伊兹先生 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后有联络上吗 兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说兔子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎小姐好像也碰上了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊 是巴纳比的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？罗伊兹先生也会开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不怎么搞笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.69,0:18:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不反过来变成我搞笑失败了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这个故障了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能给我看一下员工证吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？昨天还过得去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 赶紧把这个可疑人物撵出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 罗伊兹先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是做了什么让你不爽的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在哪里查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别随便叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们到警务室去谈谈后续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对 我说啊 我是英雄..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 今天的早晨也是那么舒畅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刚才那人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 用你那双眼睛好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狂野..猛虎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很明白嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我到里边去..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副胡子+那个眼罩 谁都能扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不少呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样假扮英雄企图混进大楼里的.. 所谓的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是所谓的粉丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GoodMorning~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！开始了 英雄紧急特别节目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底会把怎样的逮捕剧展现给我们看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊喂 一点联络都没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的目标是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯NEXT 鏑木·T·虎彻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他涉嫌杀害现居住于斯特恩比尔特的68岁女士 萨曼莎·泰勒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被认为是凶器的火钩子以及凶杀现场的被害人家中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检测出鏑木·T·虎彻的指纹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在紧急通缉中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是一层大厅 发现通缉犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急请求增援！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你等一下 这一定是个误会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下 听好了 别开枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎阿姨她？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏑木·T·虎彻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏑木..T..虎彻？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨曼莎阿姨..明明还没回报过您什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以过来 小枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:15.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据报嫌疑犯鏑木·T·虎彻就在刚刚被目击出现于EastBronze 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:17.28,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各社英雄虽然已经出动 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于他是个拥有危险能力的NEXT的可能性极高 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:22.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据预测有可能出现新的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.02,0:23:26.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临近的各位居民请务必提高警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真实也消失在黑暗之中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs44}大家好 我是Tiger&Bunny中喜欢把粉丝信带回家欣赏的那位 虎彻是也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能是犯人..哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.78,0:24:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 基友英雄传
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.14,0:24:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家一起念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,heaven..helps..those...
